{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e68d281c9f","title":"中共中央关于同意浙江省政府公布六大禁令给华东局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fbd28180bf","index":0,"year":1950,"month":2,"day":15,"articleId":"e68d281c9f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fa8171b10b","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于同意浙江省政府公布六大禁令给华东局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"f71b1e1b01","type":"appellation","text":"华东局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"bac4d8bacb","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十三日电悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"7246a1e38e","type":"paragraph","text":"同意浙江省政府立即公布六大禁令，以停止混乱现象。省委及群众团体同时应将此项禁令通知全党及各团体严格执行。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"e67903b09b","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央二月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"15c6bcd47f","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"2ccf933314","type":"subtitle","text":"华东局关于同意浙江省公布六大禁令的请示","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"5fe9ae8f98","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九五O年二月十三日）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"a005790915","type":"appellation","text":"中央：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"70e9917712","type":"paragraph","text":"浙江省掌握政策较差，混乱现象较严重。根据前年山东经验，由省府公布六大禁令的单行法，收效较大。我们对浙江省省委所拟六大禁令，拟予同意。请中央审查批示。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"1cea2b97f0","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）禁止任何人、任何机关团体擅自逮捕人犯。凡未奉县以上人民政府命令，无逮捕现行犯以外的其他任何人犯之权，违者定予惩处。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"8a30d3d09f","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）禁止任何人乱打犯人，违者定予惩处。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"d29b8dc9be","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）禁止任何机关，未经人民政府法庭判处，未经省人民政府批准处决人犯。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"64ba64db8b","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）禁止任何机关团体及县以下区、乡人民政府，借故向人民摊派、征用财物及一切额外负担。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"9b4643f732","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）禁止任何机关团体人员贪污浪费、破坏、霸占、盗卖公粮、公物及一切国家财产。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"14c2447ccf","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）禁止私占或贪污浪费、破坏、盗卖群众斗争果实。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"},{"id":"0a4f733cf4","type":"paragraph","text":" 华东局丑元","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f"}],"page":{"id":"cdd60622f2","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e68d281c9f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}